  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8eb9d9fa0ccbe1b4cbcd2a1d889b806b, type: 3}
  m_Name: FirstDayConvo04
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Dialogue
  conversationName: FirstDayMainConversation
  lines:
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: There is no need for thanks-- just make good use of that tool, and don't
      botch any harvesting.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: Hm? Oh yes, it takes skill to harvest materials without <b>damaging the
      goods</b>. Make sure you are <i>careful and precise</i> while extracting.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: If the goods are not of <b>high quality</b>, the customers will not pay
      a high price for them. Selling high quality products will make it easier to
      reach quota.
  - speakerName: Randy
    line: Now, with all of that out of the way, here-- take this <b>room key</b>.
      Use that to unlock the door to one of the guest rooms, so that you can enter
      and begin harvesting.
  repeatLine:
    speakerName: Randy
    line: Don't you have something else better to do?
